The paper discusses state estimation for legged robots, which falls under the robotics (cs.RO) sub-category. The paper also uses optimization techniques, which are commonly used in machine learning (cs.LG) and control systems (cs.SY) research. Finally, the paper proposes a new method for state estimation, which falls under the artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-category.
